snippet.title: Hungry Meem | 1st Trailer
snippet.description:
“Hungry Meem”, the brand-new Colony Simulation Game 
To be released on Steam® and Nintendo Switch in 2025!

Help the hungry critters called Meems and lead them to a happier life!
Add to your Steam Wishlist now!

Official Site : https://hungrymeem.com/en
Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/3051240
Nintendo Switch : www.cloudedleopardent.com/en/news/5024

Please follow us to be notified of the latest news about the title!
Official X (Japanese) : https://x.com/hungrymeem_JP
Official X (English) : https://x.com/hungrymeem
